🌟GitOps🌟
About of GitOps?
 📂 GitOps utilizes Git as the primary source of truth for managing and delivering application infrastructure. 🔄 🌐 GitOps implements Continuous Deployment for☁️cloud-native applications. 🤖 One of the primary objectives of GitOps📦 is to automate the development process.⚙️

Gains From GitOps:-
🔒 Version Control Management
🛡️ Enhanced Security
🌐 Centralized Management via Git
🤖 Automated Processes
🕵️‍♂️ Improved Transparency
✔️ Quality Checks
⏪ Easy Rollback Capability
🧭 Impeccable Traceability